1. *U obliku* srca sam ti dao poklon. (In the shape of, I gave you a gift in the shape of a heart.)
2. Naša kompanija nudi proizvode *u obliku* tableta i kapsula. (Our company offers products in the form of tablets and capsules.)
3. *Oblikom* ovaj sto je vrlo sličan onom u mom domu. (In terms of shape, this table is very similar to the one in my home.)
4. Moramo dati *oblik* ovom projektu pre nego što krenemo dalje. (We need to give shape to this project before we move forward.)
5. Njen lik je *oblikovan* mnogim životnim iskustvima. (Her character has been shaped by many life experiences.)
6. Ova stvarnost je *oblikovana* našim mislima i delima. (This reality is shaped by our thoughts and actions.)
7. Pogledajte *oblik* ovog stakla - vrlo je jednostavan i elegantan. (Look at the shape of this glass - it's very simple and elegant.)
8. Zanima me *oblikovanje* budućnosti našeg grada. (I'm interested in shaping the future of our city.)
9. *Oblikujemo* ovu ideju kako bismo je učinili privlačnijom za investitore. (We are shaping this idea to make it more attractive to investors.)
10. *Obliku* ovog problema treba pristupiti na drugačiji način. (The shape of this problem needs to be approached in a different way.)